Properties.Name: Text
Properties.Value: This Workflow pages through ElevenLabs agents and their conversations using cursors, then pulls each conversation's details (including analysis) to check whether contact info was captured via Data Collection. It maps first_name, last_name, email, and phone into a HubSpot CRM payload to create a contact, creates the contact, and logs each attempt as a success or error.
